_:N3925fef44b754123a95875bbf295ba58 <http://schema.org/name> "Paul Robson" .
_:N3925fef44b754123a95875bbf295ba58 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Paul joined Sellafield in 1979 and has held a wide variety of leadership roles, including the commissioning of the waste vitrification lines and operations within existing nuclear facilities.</p>\n\n<p>His most recent role was head of the Site Ion Exchange Effluent Plant (SIXEP) programme where he established a clear strategy and business case to support future operations.</p>\n\n<p>In addition to leadership roles, he has been a member of the Nuclear Safety Committee since 2015.</p>\n\n" .
